<P ID="14"><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Torch</ENAMEX> said he had received several comments from residents about the problems with loud music and street racing <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">this past weekend</TIMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Torch</ENAMEX> said he was even amazed to hear during <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Sunday</TIMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">night</TIMEX>'s power outage that people were still able to play loud music.
